overview: On July 8th World Series Wrestling presents the first night of its Phoenix Rising Tour straight from Adelaide Oval in Australia.  The event features the international superstar "Always Ready" Matt Cardona, current AEW sensations Johnny Superstar, Buddy Matthews and Brian Cage, ROH World Champion Jon Gresham, direct from the NJPW BosJ Tournament Alex Zayne, 'The Bad Boy' Joey Janela, Impact Wrestling star Trey Miguel, Flip Gordon, current AAA Reina de Reinas Champion Taya Valkyrie and Impact Wrestling Knockouts Chelsea Green and Tenille Dashwood, plus Australia's top pro wrestling stars!  Get Ready for the Ride of Your Life!
title: World Series Wrestling: Phoenix Rising (Night 1)
